                <p>We’re inching closer to <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/amazon-prime-day-deals/">Prime Day</a>, but you don’t have to wait until July 8 to save a few bucks on some of the best video game-inspired plushies around. <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0BXB87T6C,B0842QTCZ8,B07PPVR3RH,B07D9MT2JK,B08BXR2CWK,B08BNSP2DH,B08S3BK5HW,B0BXFRTZF6,B0C1HSCQPR,B09QH6G8BX,B08BNW4L25,B0BS9ZDD74,B0BS9YPJ9C,B08S2RYKVR,B09C75MF1G,B08X1JLS5S,B08X1YSQG1,B08BXR4DL1,B0BF5XSRQ2,B0C81L31LX,B0BHCCBDY2,B0B9YH5RDG,B0BHCCP6KD&amp;tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Tomy's Club Mocchi-Mocchi collection</a> is filled with ultra-soft, officially licensed plushies themed around Super Mario, The Legend of Zelda, Kirby, Animal Crossing, and more popular franchises.</p><p>While many of the standouts hail from classic Nintendo franchises, one of our favorites is the 15-inch Cuphead plush. Fans can get this <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Club-Mocchi-Mocchi-Cuphead-Plush-Collectible/dp/B0BXB87T6C?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">very cute Cuphead plush for $27 (was $35) at Amazon</a>. This is the lowest price ever for Club Mocchi-Mocchi's Cuphead plush, which is large and chunky enough to be used as a pillow.</p><div title="[Various] Cuphead Club Mocchi-Mocchi Plush" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="3768" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="[Various] Cuphead Club Mocchi-Mocchi Plush" data-collection="">             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Club-Mocchi-Mocchi-Cuphead-Plush-Collectible/dp/B0BXB87T6C?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Club-Mocchi-Mocchi-Cuphead-Plush-Collectible\/dp\/B0BXB87T6C?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Club-Mocchi-Mocchi-Cuphead-Plush-Collectible/dp/B0BXB87T6C?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">Cuphead 15-Inch Plush by Club Mocchi-Mocchi</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Club-Mocchi-Mocchi-Cuphead-Plush-Collectible/dp/B0BXB87T6C?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Club-Mocchi-Mocchi-Cuphead-Plush-Collectible\/dp\/B0BXB87T6C?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Club-Mocchi-Mocchi-Cuphead-Plush-Collectible/dp/B0BXB87T6C?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">$27 (was $35)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>Cuphead displays a wide range of facial expressions in StudioMDHR's brilliant boss rush action game--and in Netflix's TV adaptation--but Club Mocchi-Mocchi opted for happiness with its officially licensed 15-inch plush. The result is an adorable recreation of the beloved character.</p><p>Since Cuphead's <em>cup head </em>has a handle on the back, you could attach it to your backpack to have the world's largest keychain plush. In all seriousness, it's worth noting that this plush topples over if you try to display it without a support behind it. And yes, it's because Cuphead has an enormous head.</p><p>Cuphead isn't the only large Club Mocchi-Mocchi plush available for a discount. Check out deals on Nintendo and Sega designs below.</p></div>                      </div><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4522659-plushies.png" data-ref-id="1300-4522659" data-ratio="0.563" data-width="1000" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4522659-plushies.png" data-ref-id="1300-4522659"></a><figcaption>Club Mocchi-Mocchi 15-inch gaming plushies</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4522659-plushies.png"></figure><h2><a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0BXB87T6C,B0842QTCZ8,B07PPVR3RH,B07D9MT2JK,B08BXR2CWK,B08BNSP2DH,B08S3BK5HW,B0BXFRTZF6,B0C1HSCQPR,B09QH6G8BX,B08BNW4L25,B0BS9ZDD74,B0BS9YPJ9C,B08S2RYKVR,B09C75MF1G,B08X1JLS5S,B08X1YSQG1,B08BXR4DL1,B0BF5XSRQ2,B0C81L31LX,B0BHCCBDY2,B0B9YH5RDG,B0BHCCP6KD&amp;tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Club Mocchi Mocchi Plush Deals</a></h2><p>Other great deals on 15-inch plushies at Amazon include <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Club-Mocchi-Nintendo-Collectible-Plushies/dp/B0842QTCZ8?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Super Mario's Goomba</a> for $24.49, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mocchi-Nintendo-Mario-Shell-Stuffed/dp/B07D9MT2JK?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mario Kart's Blue Shell</a> for $22.50, and <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Club-Mocchi-Legend-Zelda-Stuffed/dp/B08BNW4L25?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Zelda's Octorok</a> for $23. The list below also includes a few deals from Best Buy, Walmart, and Target. You can get a <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Biggest+And+Best+Cuphead+Plush+Drops+To+Lowest+Price+Yet&amp;fnauthor=stevenpetite&amp;fndate=2025-06-27+13%3A04%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-06-27+13%3A05%3A07&amp;fnarticle_id=6532788&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fbestbuy.7tiv.net%2FRGE66b&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fclub-mocchi-mocchi-nintendo-plush-amazon-deals%2F1100-6532788%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">15-inch Yoshi Egg plush</a> at Best Buy for $21 and 6-inch <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Biggest+And+Best+Cuphead+Plush+Drops+To+Lowest+Price+Yet&amp;fnauthor=stevenpetite&amp;fndate=2025-06-27+13%3A04%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-06-27+13%3A05%3A07&amp;fnarticle_id=6532788&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.walmart.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F565706%2F9383%3Fveh%3Daff%26sourceid%3Dimp_000011112222333344%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FClub-Mocchi-Mocchi-Animal-Crossing-Tom-Nook-Junior-6-inch-Plush-Stuffed-Toy-Super-Soft-Great-for-Kids-and-Collectors%2F324998323%26subId1%3Dsubid_value&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fclub-mocchi-mocchi-nintendo-plush-amazon-deals%2F1100-6532788%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Animal Crossing plushies</a> for $10 at Walmart. Target has a <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Biggest+And+Best+Cuphead+Plush+Drops+To+Lowest+Price+Yet&amp;fnauthor=stevenpetite&amp;fndate=2025-06-27+13%3A04%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-06-27+13%3A05%3A07&amp;fnarticle_id=6532788&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fg