;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Club-Mocchi-Mocchi-Kirby-Plushies/dp/B0DQ9TKWBW?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">Ginormous Sleeping Friend Kirby (35 x 28 Inches)</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Club-Mocchi-Mocchi-Kirby-Plushies/dp/B0DQ9TKWBW?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Club-Mocchi-Mocchi-Kirby-Plushies\/dp\/B0DQ9TKWBW?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Club-Mocchi-Mocchi-Kirby-Plushies/dp/B0DQ9TKWBW?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">$150 | Limited to 1,500 Kirbys</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>While it’s not on sale, the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Club-Mocchi-Mocchi-Kirby-Plushies/dp/B0DQ9TKWBW?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Suya Suya Friend Kirby</a> is one of the coolest plushies in Club Mocchi-Mocchi's collection. At 35 inches long and 28 inches wide, this very tired Kirby is large enough to serve as a soft floor chair in your game room.</p><p>Given its enormity, Suya Suya Friend Kirby is very expensive at $150. It's also limited edition, as Club Mocchi-Mocchi